name: Toy Story [SNES]
description:
Toy Story is a puzzle game developed by Traveller's Tales, Disney Interactive, small and Tiertex Design Studios. It came out on 01-01-1995. It was published by small. The game is rated as "Recommended" on RAWG.
Toy Story is available on SNES, NES, Game Boy and Genesis.
It was scored by Allister Brimble, Andy Blythe and Marten Joustra.
